snippet.title: Celebrity Lawyer Areva Martin On Johnny Depp's Divorce From Amber Heard | Good Morning Britain
snippet.description:

Celebrity lawyer Areva Martin talks about how she expects the tumultuous divorce between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard to play out.
